Package org.jlinalg.field_p

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FieldP<RE extends FieldP<RE>>
    This class represents an element of the modulo p field Fp (i.e. the Galois field GF(p)) where p is prime.
    FieldPAbstractFactory<RE extends FieldP<RE>>
    This class defines the abstract class for actual implementations of FieldP.
    FieldPBig
    This class implements an element of Fp where p can be arbitrarily big by using BigIntegers.
    FieldPBigFactory  
    FieldPFactoryComparator<T>  
    FieldPFactoryMap
    Cash for instances of polynomial factories.
    FieldPLong
    This class implements the operations in Fp where p < PRIME_SEPARATION_BOUNDARY.
    FieldPLongFactory
    An implementation of a factory for FieldP's using "long"s as internal number type.
